        <visual name="visual"><geometry><box><size>0.2 10 1.2</size></box></geometry><material><ambient>0.35 0.35 0.35 1</ambient><diffuse>0.35 0.35 0.35 1</diffuse></material></visual>
      </link>
      <link name="north_extension_west_wall">
